name: Do It Yourself Action Collection
description: The Do It Yourself Actions are a collection of simple practical actions that can be brushed on exactly where needed - much like in Lightroom. They are great time savers and easy to use. You will also get 5 Bonus actions (these are not brush-on ones) that are pretty awesome and will intensify and pop colors. 15 Practical Brush-On Actions: Lighten Up, Darken, Eye See You, Bye Bye Red, Lovely Skin, Adjust Temperature, Sharpen, Contrast, Color Pop, Remove Color, Adjust Black, Anti-Yellow Skin, Shiny Brown hair, Remove Tan, Tanning Bed 5 Bonus Actions: Intense, Intense Matte, Intense Moonlight, Intense Hazel, Intense Romance The actions are tested in CS2-5 and come with a layer mask tutorial. A version for Photoshop Elements will be released shortly. PLEASE NOTE: The files will be e-mailed to you after your purchase. While this is done as soon as possible, please allow up to 24hours of processing time. You will also receive simple instructions on how to use your actions, but a previous basic knowledge of Photoshop is necessary.

name: Shirley Collection - Photoshop Actions
description:
The Shirley Collection includes 28 practical and artsy actions to enhance your images and save you time! 

Each action targets a different color, works on a different aspect of your image, and enhances it in a unique way. The Shirley Collection is designed to cover all your editing needs in one action collection. 

The Shirley Collection is also a great time saver for advanced editors and a valuable help for beginners.

Tested in Photoshop CS2-5 and Elements 8 and up.

name: Storyboard "Catherine" - 10x20
description:
A 10x20 storyboard template in 300dpi. It is fully layered and comes with clipping masks for quick and easy insertion of images. The color blocks can also be changed as necessary.

Tested in Photoshop CS2-5 and Elements 9-10.

PLEASE NOTE: The psd files will be e-mailed to you after your purchase. While this is done as soon as possible, please allow up to 24hours of processing time. You will also receive simple instructions on how to use your template, but a previous basic knowledge of Photoshop is necessary.

name: Simple Chic Album Template - For 12x12inch Albums
description:
"Simple Chic" Album template in 300dpi. You will receive 11 unique and fully layered psd files (2 album pages per file) with clipping masks for easy insertion of images. The background as well as the placement of each picture and the text can be customized.

All layouts are displayed and all pages match each other in style for a consistent overall look.

The headers were created with a wedding theme in mind, but they can be changed to fit any theme or simply be removed. You can use solid colors, digital papers, and/or your own images to customize each layer!

Designed to work with WHCC's 12x12inch 20-page Albums on watercolor, linen, recycled, or satin paper. Can be printed through other labs with minor adjustments. Easily re-size to a 6x6inch album.

PLEASE NOTE: These psd files will be e-mailed to you after your purchase. While this is done as soon as possible, please allow up to 24hours of processing time. You will also receive simple instructions on how to use your templates, but a previous basic knowledge of Photoshop is necessary.
